      },
      "frameId": "f-1",
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p>Run a collaborative impact–effort exercise with your team — drag stickies, debate impact and effort, and overlay team excitement with dot voting.</p><p><br /></p><p>When you’re done, the flow turns the messy board into a clean, structured, prioritized task table.<br /><br /></p><p>A fast way to go from visual exploration to an actionable backlog — aligned with team energy and clear prioritization logic.</p>"
    },
